title: COAST ORB / reeds with buoy

dialogueTree.text: That patch of reeds over there -- it's a great place to hide something. Kind of out of the way, being so close to the water.

links.text: Wait, I can't see anything interesting...

links.title: Inland Empire: "You don't have a reason to -- yet."
links.text: You don't have a reason to -- yet.

links.text: Nothing. Just a hunch. The hunch passes, leaving you there, by the old buoy bobbing in the water. Time to go.
